data.description: Kingwood patio home with a pool and a separate courtyard. The living room has high ceilings and large windows on both sides with views to the pool and the courtyard. The primary bedroom is situated on the first floor with a large primary bath, dual sinks, separate shower, soaking tub, and large walk-in closet. The 2 secondary beds are located on the 2nd floor. Kingwood Country Club is just around the corner. Enjoy a short walk to the neighborhood lake for a stunning sunset. Room sizes are approximate, please measure for accuracy.
